  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nI'd love to see a [liveness endpoint](https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/pull/131) implemented, at `/eth/v1/validator/liveness`. This would make it possible to use the doppelganger protection in a  Lighthouse validator client with Teku, and thus Infura.\r\n",
